{
  "stem": "1292.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember one girl-- one woman-- young woman and her husband, they brought the-- in a box, in a matchbox, they brought some German earth with them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they absolutely-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were so-- well, who could have dreamed that such a thing can happen?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, it was absolutely beyond us, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- then ghetto was formed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just let me think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think ghetto was formed 1940.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't hold me to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some dates, you know, in those unhappy memories, I really did try to separate so much, and I am not very good with dates.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But maybe somebody else will be more helpful about the dates.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I think the ghetto was formed end of 1940.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the Kazimierz, that was the part where the Jewish people did live, they did have to all-- they was evacuated and come to Podgorze, where actually was my-- where I did live before.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, they crowd us very much into a ghetto, which was-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] it was isolated-- very-- physically with some-- what you call it?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wires, yes?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they crowd three families in or four families in one place where before one family did work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In your house?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you stay in that house?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, all my aunts and all-- they crowded into our place, but I married 1940 in August and then I was put together-- we didn't-- we didn't live together, my husband.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was my family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We live with another family, and then later, again, with another family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was one, two, three rooms, and there was for families living there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's amazing the spirit of the people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, in the beginning it was-- well, it was gradually worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
